{"tid":1916922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少女時代太妍過31歲生日！父親同日傳噩耗：心肌梗塞過世","createTime":"2020-03-09T07:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T09:10:30.000Z","uid":6783,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3232261a6b42859fc8b8a5d82f5cd56d9180749d","tid":1916922,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"記者吳孟庭／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓女團少女時代的太妍今（9）日過生日，本來應該是開心慶祝的日子，稍早卻傳來悲傷消息，父親早上因為心肌梗塞，不幸離開人世，據悉她聽聞消息後慌忙與母親、哥哥與妹妹會合，而她的所屬經紀公司SM娛樂也證實消息，並表示葬禮將會與遺族一起安靜地舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月9日是太妍滿31歲的生日，也是她即將發行新歌《HAPPY》的日子，她2天前就在IG上倒數寫「HAPPY 3/9」，非常期待這天的到來，粉絲也都留言慶祝。沒想到稍早南韓媒體《edaily》報導，太妍父親早上因為急性心肌梗塞過世，她也是接到消息後，趕忙與家人見面。<br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂證實消息表示，太妍父親的葬禮將會與家族一起安靜地舉行，而太妍這段期間將與家族在一起守喪，因此原本預定發行的新單曲，以及本來要進行的VLIVE直播也宣布延期。"},{"pid":"5630d572c37bf502bcfd3d94c3ed5b44edde1dd7","tid":1916922,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"HAPPY 3/9..."},{"pid":"691249b6f1834e97ff4a1b6d97f353d5724eabd9","tid":1916922,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"5630d572c37bf502bcfd3d94c3ed5b44edde1dd7","tid":1916922,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"HAPPY 3/9..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KHBhEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KHBhEQ.png&h=4f2d8263&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a9d3bfb0bcbc4a51990d2144f4aceb011266ea4","tid":1916922,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"691249b6f1834e97ff4a1b6d97f353d5724eabd9","tid":1916922,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"5630d572c37bf502bcfd3d94c3ed5b44edde1dd7","tid":1916922,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"HAPPY 3/9..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KHBhEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=